      <div data-module="ga4-link-tracker" class="gem-c-step-nav-related gem-c-step-nav-related--singular">
    <h2 class="gem-c-step-nav-related__heading">
      <span class="gem-c-step-nav-related__pretitle"><span class='govuk-visually-hidden'>This page is</span> Part of</span>
          <a href="/export-goods"
            class="govuk-link gem-print-force-link-styles"
              data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"part of","index_link":"1","index_total":"1","section":"Part of"}'
            >
            Export goods from the UK: step by step
          </a>
        </h2>
</div>

      <div data-module="gemstepnav ga4-event-tracker" data-show-text="Show" data-hide-text="Hide" data-show-all-text="Show all steps" data-hide-all-text="Hide all steps" data-ga4-expandable="" data-id="b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb" class="gem-c-step-nav js-hidden govuk-!-display-none-print" title="Export goods from the UK: step by step">
    <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__steps">
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="check-if-you-need-to-follow-this-process"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="1">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-label govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden">Step</span> 1<span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-colon govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Check if you need to follow this process
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-check-if-you-need-to-follow-this-process-1" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":1,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Check if you need to follow this process"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">Follow these steps if you&#39;re moving goods permanently from: </p>

              <ul class="gem-c-step-nav__list gem-c-step-nav__list--choice" data-length="2"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item ">England, Wales or Scotland (Great Britain) to a country outside the UK</li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item ">Northern Ireland to a country outside the UK and the EU</li></ul>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">What you need to do is different if you are:</p>

              <ul class="gem-c-step-nav__list gem-c-step-nav__list--choice" data-length="4"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a rel="external" data-position="1.3" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/trading-and-moving-goods-in-and-out-of-northern-ireland-from-1-january-2021">moving goods between Great Britain and Northern Ireland or Northern Ireland and the EU </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a rel="external" data-position="1.4" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="https://personal.help.royalmail.com/app/answers/detail/a_id/106">sending goods through the post (Royal Mail guidance) </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="1.5" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/take-goods-sell-abroad?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">taking a small amount of goods personally to sell abroad </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="1.6" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/taking-goods-out-uk-temporarily?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">taking goods temporarily out of the UK </a></li></ul>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a rel="external" data-position="1.7" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="https://www.business.gov.uk/export-from-uk/learn/categories/">Learn about exporting, including making export plans, on Business.gov.uk </a></li></ol>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="check-the-rules-for-exporting-your-goods"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="2">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-label govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden">Step</span> 2<span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-colon govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Check the rules for exporting your goods
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-check-the-rules-for-exporting-your-goods-2" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":2,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Check the rules for exporting your goods"}'>
              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="2.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/check-duties-customs-exporting?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Check duties, rules and restrictions for your goods in the destination country </a></li></ol>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="apply-for-any-licences-you-need-to-export-your-goods"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="3">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--logic">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      and
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Apply for any licences you need to export your goods
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-apply-for-any-licences-you-need-to-export-your-goods-3" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":3,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Apply for any licences you need to export your goods"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">There are special rules and you may need to get licences or certificates if you are exporting any of the following:</p>

              <ul class="gem-c-step-nav__list gem-c-step-nav__list--choice" data-length="14"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/government/collections/guidance-on-exporting-live-animals-or-animal-products?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">animals and animal products </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.2" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/government/collections/importing-and-exporting-plants-and-plant-products?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">plants and plant products </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.3" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/export-drugs-and-medicines-special-rules?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">drugs and medicines </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.4" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/export-medical-devices-special-rules?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">medical devices </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.5" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/export-chemicals-licences-and-special-rules?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">chemicals </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.6" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/applying-for-a-licence-to-import-or-export-ozone-depleting-substances?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">ozone-depleting substances and F-gases </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.7" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/controls-on-radioactive-sources?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">radioactive substances </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.8" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/export-diamonds-special-rules?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">diamonds </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.9" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/export-art-antiques-and-cultural-goods-special-rules?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">art works, antiques and culturally significant goods </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.10" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/importing-and-exporting-waste?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">waste shipments </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.11" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/controls-on-torture-goods?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">goods that could be used for torture or capital punishment </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.12" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/firearms-and-export-control-forms?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">firearms, ammunition and related equipment </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.13" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/export-controls-military-goods-software-and-technology?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">military goods, services and technology </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="3.14" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/export-controls-dual-use-items-software-and-technology-goods-for-torture-and-radioactive-sources?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">items that can have both civil and military uses </a></li></ul>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="get-your-business-ready-to-export"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="4">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-label govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden">Step</span> 3<span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-colon govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Get your business ready to export
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-get-your-business-ready-to-export-4" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":4,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Get your business ready to export"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">You need an EORI number that starts with GB to export goods from England, Wales or Scotland.</p>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">If you move goods to or from Northern Ireland you may need one that starts with XI.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="4.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/eori?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Get an EORI number </a></li></ol>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="4.2" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/vat-registration/when-to-register?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Check if you need to register for VAT </a></li></ol>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">There are processes that can make clearing customs quicker and easier to manage if you export goods regularly.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="3"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="4.3" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/using-simplified-declarations-for-exports?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Find out about using simplified declaration procedures </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="4.4" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/what-you-need-to-move-goods-between-or-through-common-transit-countries-including-the-eu?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Check if you can use Common Transit to move your goods </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="4.5" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/authorised-economic-operator-certification?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Check if Authorised Economic Operator status is right for you </a></li></ol>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="check-whoever-s-receiving-the-goods-can-import-them"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="5">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--logic">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      and
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Check whoever&#39;s receiving the goods can import them
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-check-whoever-s-receiving-the-goods-can-import-them-5" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":5,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Check whoever&#39;s receiving the goods can import them"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">The business or person receiving the goods may need:</p>

              <ul class="gem-c-step-nav__list gem-c-step-nav__list--choice" data-length="2"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item ">to make an import declaration in their country</li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item ">licences or certificates to receive goods from the UK</li></ul>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">Check whoever you are sending the goods to is able to import them into their country.</p>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="decide-who-will-make-export-declarations-and-transport-the-goods"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="6">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-label govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden">Step</span> 4<span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-colon govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Decide who will make export declarations and transport the goods
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-decide-who-will-make-export-declarations-and-transport-the-goods-6" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":6,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Decide who will make export declarations and transport the goods"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">You can hire someone to deal with customs and transport the goods for you, or you can do it yourself. </p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="3"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="6.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/appoint-someone-to-deal-with-customs-on-your-behalf?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Find out how to hire someone to deal with customs for you </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="6.2" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/export-customs-declaration?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Find out how to make export declarations yourself </a></li><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="6.3" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/transport-goods-from-uk-by-road?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Find out how to transport goods out of the UK by road </a></li></ol>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="classify-your-goods"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="7">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-label govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden">Step</span> 5<span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-colon govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Classify your goods
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-classify-your-goods-7" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":7,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Classify your goods"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">You must find the right commodity code to classify the goods you&#39;re exporting.</p>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">Your customs agent or transporter might be able to help you with this.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="7.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/finding-commodity-codes-for-imports-or-exports?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Find the right commodity code for your goods </a></li></ol>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          gem-c-step-nav__step--active"
           aria-current="step"
          data-show
          id="prepare-the-invoice-and-other-documentation-for-your-goods"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="8">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-label govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden">Step</span> 6<span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-colon govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Prepare the invoice and other documentation for your goods
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-prepare-the-invoice-and-other-documentation-for-your-goods-8" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":8,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Prepare the invoice and other documentation for your goods"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">The completed invoice and any licences or certificates must travel with the goods.</p>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">When filling in the value of your goods on the invoice, use the price you’re selling them for. If you&#39;re not selling the goods, use the market value of the goods. List any freight or export insurance you included in the price separately.</p>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">You may need proof of origin if exporting to a country where your goods have a reduced or zero rate of duty.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item gem-c-step-nav__list-item--active"><a data-position="8.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="#content"><span class="gem-c-step-nav__link-active-context visuallyhidden">You are currently viewing: </span>Get proof of origin for your goods </a></li></ol>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">You might be able to zero rate the goods for VAT. This means you can charge your customers VAT at 0%.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="8.2" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/vat-on-goods-exported-from-the-uk-notice-703?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Check if you can zero rate the goods for VAT </a></li></ol>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="get-your-goods-through-customs"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="9">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-label govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden">Step</span> 7<span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-colon govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Get your goods through customs
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-get-your-goods-through-customs-9" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":9,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Get your goods through customs"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">If you&#39;ve appointed someone to deal with UK customs for you, they&#39;ll make the declaration and get your goods through the UK border.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="9.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/export-customs-declaration?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Make an export declaration and get your goods cleared by UK customs </a></li></ol>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">You may need other documentation to get your goods into the destination country. Ask the person or business buying your goods what information you need to provide.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="9.2" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/guidance/returning-goods-to-the-uk?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Check how to bring goods back into the UK if they were rejected for import at another country’s border </a></li></ol>

</div>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-step-nav__step js-step
          "
          
          
          id="keep-invoices-and-records"
          data-track-count="stepNavSection"
          >
          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__header js-toggle-panel" data-position="10">
            <h3 class="gem-c-step-nav__title">
              <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle gem-c-step-nav__circle--number">
                <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-inner">
                  <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-background">
                      <span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-label govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden">Step</span> 8<span class="gem-c-step-nav__circle-step-colon govuk-!-display-none-print visuallyhidden" aria-hidden="true">:</span>
                  </span>
                </span>
              </span>

              <span class="js-step-title">
                Keep invoices and records
              </span>
</h3>          </div>


          <div class="gem-c-step-nav__panel js-panel" id="step-panel-keep-invoices-and-records-10" data-module="ga4-link-tracker" data-ga4-set-indexes="" data-ga4-link='{"event_name":"navigation","type":"step by step","index_section":10,"index_section_count":10,"section":"Keep invoices and records"}'>
              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">You must keep commercial invoices and any customs paperwork. </p>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">If you&#39;re VAT registered, record the goods in your VAT accounts even if they are zero-rated.</p>

              <ol class="gem-c-step-nav__list " data-length="1"><li class="gem-c-step-nav__list-item js-list-item "><a data-position="10.1" class="gem-c-step-nav__link js-link" href="/charge-reclaim-record-vat/keeping-vat-records?step-by-step-nav=b9347000-c726-4c3c-b76a-e52b6cebb3eb">Find out how to record the goods in your VAT accounts </a></li></ol>

              <p class="gem-c-step-nav__paragraph">If you exported controlled goods, for example firearms, keep the paperwork that shows who owns the goods.</p>

</div>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>


</div>
</div>

</div>


    </main>
  </div>

  


